Various things!

247
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:57,170
[Overflowing Kindness and Benevolence]

248
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:16,000
You tramp, you dare come here?

249
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:19,350
I'm here to help you, mind your attitude.

250
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:24,330
Liuli! Shanhu's wedding fell through.

251
00:17:24,330 --> 00:17:26,700
She can't help but be a little upset.

252
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:31,070
We are one family, we should help each other.

253
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:33,130
One family?

254
00:17:34,670 --> 00:17:36,890
A'Ye! You go guard outside!

255
00:17:36,890 --> 00:17:39,440
Report immediately if people are here.

256
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:46,400
One family?

257
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:49,460
Not long ago, Mister Kudi locked his door and refused to see me.

258
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:52,190
How are you saying that we are a family?

259
00:17:52,190 --> 00:17:54,850
Once today's catastrophe is done, you will still be with yourselves.

260
00:17:54,850 --> 00:17:57,450
I will still remain by myself. We won't interfere in each other's lives.

261
00:17:57,450 --> 00:18:01,340
That's the best that could happen. It seems like a new you.

262
00:18:08,490 --> 00:18:12,490
Back then, Madam Cao and Father thought of a way to make my mom sign a divorce certificate.

263
00:18:12,490 --> 00:18:14,500
You kicked us out of the Kudi family.

264
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:17,660
I didn't think that my mother's belonging,

265
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:20,390
would still be your jewels.

266
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:24,250
Father, this bracelet is mine.

267
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:27,920
Since you guys like it this much then help me take care of it.

268
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:32,030
When you're ready to return then beg me.

269
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,770
Daughter, stay please.

270
00:18:33,770 --> 00:18:37,010
A'Cao, quickly give Madam An's belongings back to Liuli.

271
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:39,620
Let's not suffer a great loss for something so small.

272
00:18:43,420 --> 00:18:45,880
That year I also didnâ€™t have a choice.

273
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:50,460
We're not going to give all of Kudi's house just because of you, are we?

274
00:19:00,850 --> 00:19:02,650
Shanhu!

275
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:15,350
You hit me!

276
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:19,220
Don't hit! Don't fight!

277
00:19:19,220 --> 00:19:22,470
You hurt my hand badly yesterday.

278
00:19:22,470 --> 00:19:26,750
I lost some strength, I couldn't hit as hard as I wanted.

279
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:31,640
Madam! Madam! The one proposing is coming.

280
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,390
They're almost at the door.

281
00:19:33,390 --> 00:19:35,980
You stall at the door. The longer the better.

282
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,630
Yes!

283
00:19:38,470 --> 00:19:40,060
It's all because your mother spoiled you.

284
00:19:40,060 --> 00:19:41,590
Quick give these things to her.

285
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:44,050
Father!

286
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:52,200
Daughter, do you really have a way to cancel both proposals?

287
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:55,490
Plan, I have.

288
00:19:55,490 --> 00:19:59,060
But your family might not like my idea.

289
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:00,910
It doesn't matter! It doesn't matter!

290
00:20:00,910 --> 00:20:03,860
What do you mean? Do you want to hurt me again?

291
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:05,610
We are at this point already.

292
00:20:05,610 --> 00:20:08,730
Now what is important is not to anger neither House of Hedong nor House Duwei.

293
00:20:08,730 --> 00:20:11,560
We have to protect our Kudi family.

294
00:20:13,330 --> 00:20:15,260
This isn't hard.

295
00:20:15,260 --> 00:20:16,890
As long as you do as I say,

296
00:20:16,890 --> 00:20:18,840
I promise no one will be offended.

297
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:21,890
Then that's good. We'll listen to you.

298
00:20:26,090 --> 00:20:30,450
[Kudi Residence]

299
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:33,360
You can't go in!

300
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:36,150
- Matchmaker, you can't go in.
- You can't go in!

301
00:20:36,150 --> 00:20:38,520
- Let me through!
- Matchmaker!

302
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:42,240
- Matchmaker! Master isn't here.
- Faster, faster!

303
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:44,930
- Matchmaker, you really can't go in!
- Faster!

304
00:20:44,930 --> 00:20:46,830
Send it in!

305
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:52,130
Good news, good news!

306
00:20:54,810 --> 00:20:56,400
Madam.

307
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:59,740
Congratulations Madam Cao.

308
00:20:59,740 --> 00:21:02,600
House of Hedong sent me to offer betrothal gifts.

309
00:21:03,690 --> 00:21:06,060
Matchmaker, you worked hard to come here.

310
00:21:06,060 --> 00:21:08,600
But my husband left yesterday.

311
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:11,060
He still isn't back.

312
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:18,550
He left yesterday?

313
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:20,530
He still hasn't come back.

314
00:21:20,530 --> 00:21:23,990
Is this house trying to delay on purpose?

315
00:21:25,910 --> 00:21:27,580
Madam Cao, look carefully.

316
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:30,800
These eight boxes of betrothal gifts contain the best silk brocade.

317
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:33,710
It makes as much as betrothal gifts worthy of one hundred gold pieces.

318
00:21:33,710 --> 00:21:36,290
This is an official document, since your husband is not home,

319
00:21:36,290 --> 00:21:39,660
please sign it up for him.

320
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:43,830
(List of gifts)

321
00:22:02,010 --> 00:22:05,220
One... One hundred gold pieces...

322
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:08,390
That's... That's so much money!

323
00:22:08,390 --> 00:22:11,450
And eight boxes of silk brocade.

324
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:16,190
It's all because of you, ruining my great marriage.

325
00:22:16,190 --> 00:22:18,850
Wake up!  This originally was my wedding.

326
00:22:18,850 --> 00:22:21,490
I'm ruining my own marriage. How is it related to you?

327
00:22:21,490 --> 00:22:23,140
You...

328
00:22:23,140 --> 00:22:25,950
Fifth Madam Kudi, you are here.

329
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:30,890
Don't leave the stuff outside, carry all of them inside.

330
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:39,080
Fifth Madam.

331
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:43,150
So many things!  Put them down. We don't have enough space inside.

332
00:22:43,150 --> 00:22:44,410
Fifth Madam!

333
00:22:44,410 --> 00:22:47,460
I am here to offer the betrothal gifts on behalf of the Commandant Manor.

334
00:22:48,090 --> 00:22:51,720
Tell all of these unrelated stranger to leave.

335
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:55,390
Commandant Pei is only a fourth-ranked military official.

336
00:22:55,390 --> 00:22:58,310
How dare he compete to snatch someone from the Duke of Hedong Manor?

337
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:03,070
I wondered who it was.

338
00:23:03,070 --> 00:23:05,940
It turns out to be just a little matchmaker.

339
00:23:05,940 --> 00:23:07,670
How boastful you speak!

340
00:23:07,670 --> 00:23:10,690
You dare to compare official ranks in front of me.

341
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:14,480
If you were a noble lady dressed in purple, I'd let it go.

342
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:17,020
But you are just a higher-ranked concubine at Commandant Pei's manor.

343
00:23:17,020 --> 00:23:19,880
How dare you claim to be noble in front of me!

344
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,910
So what if it's a higher-ranked concubine?

345
00:23:21,910 --> 00:23:24,320
A high-ranked concubine is still a higher rank.

346
00:23:24,320 --> 00:23:27,400
How dare you, a little servant, be rude to me!

347
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:31,550
I may be a servant, but I'm a servant sent over by the Duke of Hedong's manor.

348
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:34,990
Today, if I let a concubine at the Commandant Manor snatch the marriage agreement from me,

349
00:23:34,990 --> 00:23:38,430
then I have wasted 20 years working as a matchmaker.

350
00:23:38,430 --> 00:23:40,110
Both of you, please calm down.

351
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,610
The Kudi family is small and lowly.

352
00:23:41,610 --> 00:23:44,830
We can't afford to offend either one of your households.

353
00:23:50,930 --> 00:23:54,090
If you don't go out yet, your mother won't be able to hold them off.

354
00:23:56,130 --> 00:23:58,130
This courtyard full of betrothal gifts

355
00:23:58,130 --> 00:24:00,850
are all prepared for me, Kudi Shanhu.

356
00:24:00,850 --> 00:24:03,050
Duke of Hedong's manor and Commandant Pei's manor

357
00:24:03,050 --> 00:24:05,190
are both here to compete

358
00:24:05,190 --> 00:24:09,630
to marry me and are almost in a battle.

359
00:24:09,630 --> 00:24:12,530
This must be the most

360
00:24:12,530 --> 00:24:14,710
glorious time in my life.

361
00:24:14,710 --> 00:24:16,700
But I have just reached the summit in my life,

362
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:19,320
it hasn't even been the time to burn half of an incense stick,
(T/N: half an hour)

363
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:22,280
I will be falling into the bottomless abyss.

364
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:24,940
Why? Why?

365
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:26,430
Hurry!

366
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:30,260
Shanhu!

367
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:32,980
Hurry, hurry! Come over here.

368
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:36,610
Come to greet your auntie and the matchmaker.

369
00:24:36,610 --> 00:24:38,850
Shanhu greets Auntie,

370
00:24:38,850 --> 00:24:41,210
and greets Madam Matchmaker.

371
00:24:41,210 --> 00:24:43,690
Shanhu, you've come at the right time. Tell her!

372
00:24:43,690 --> 00:24:46,160
Didn't you agree to go to the Commandant Manor to matchmake first?

373
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:49,270
And the proposal from Duke of Hedong's Manor came later?

374
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:51,960
So what? If a meeting for consideration counts,

375
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:53,960
why would a document and betrothal gifts be required?

376
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:57,450
Our Duke of Hedong's Manor came first with the betrothal gift.

377
00:24:57,450 --> 00:25:01,110
According to you then, anyone who wants to marry a wife or a concubine

378
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:03,740
only needs to barge into someone's family and put down the betrothal gift,

379
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,570
then it will be considered a done deal?

380
00:25:05,570 --> 00:25:07,730
No matter how high-ranking Duke of Hedong's Manor is,

381
00:25:07,730 --> 00:25:10,770
you still wouldn't win this lawsuit.

382
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:14,830
How dare a mere Commandant Manor boast to filing a lawsuit against the Duke of Hedong's Manor?

383
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:17,110
Are you afraid that the big wind will twist your tongue?
(T/N: Don't boast too much and get pushed back)

384
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:20,300
If you really want to, Duke of Hedong's Manor will not be afraid

385
00:25:20,300 --> 00:25:22,350
of meeting Commandant Manor at the Chang'an magistrate's hall.

386
00:25:22,350 --> 00:25:24,960
Put down the gift boxes, let's go!

387
00:25:25,950 --> 00:25:27,550
Wait!

388
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:31,150
Madam Matchmaker, please wait.

389
00:25:33,560 --> 00:25:37,600
What is it, have you decided to marry into the Duke of Hedong's Manor?

390
00:25:41,370 --> 00:25:45,450
Shanhu, hurry and tell her which one you'll marry.

391
00:25:46,910 --> 00:25:48,600
Kneel.

392
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,730
Auntie, you've been so kindhearted.

393
00:26:00,730 --> 00:26:03,570
I am so grateful.

394
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:10,140
But I have a bad fate and got into such a mess today.

395
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:12,690
If it turns out to be like what the matchmaker says,

396
00:26:12,690 --> 00:26:16,040
these two manors end up in the magistrate's court over marrying a concubine,

397
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:18,330
wouldn't this become a laughingstock?

398
00:26:18,330 --> 00:26:21,160
At that time, how will Auntie and Madam Matchmaker

399
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:24,750
have a good explanation for your separate masters?

400
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,850
How is this difficult to explain?

401
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:30,270
This is a marriage that was already agreed upon between related families.

402
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:32,800
If it's snatched by an outsider,

403
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:36,050
that's what's not explainable to the Commandant Manor.

404
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:42,440
Auntie, think it over carefully.

405
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:45,480
Pei Yan and Madam Cui have a good relationship.

406
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:48,070
He was really forced to marry a concubine.

407
00:26:48,070 --> 00:26:51,980
If I am taken into the manor as a concubine because of your help,

408
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:54,510
Madam Cui will definitely not be pleased with you.

409
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:57,090
If, because of the lawsuit,

410
00:26:57,090 --> 00:26:59,220
Pei Yan's career as an official is affected,

411
00:26:59,220 --> 00:27:01,670
how will Auntie be viewed

412
00:27:01,670 --> 00:27:04,130
in the manor thereafter?

413
00:27:05,150 --> 00:27:08,230
Very well said. I am different.

414
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:10,660
Being a matchmaker is my job.

415
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:12,800
I will fight till the very end.

416
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:16,320
Madam Matchmaker, the risk you take

417
00:27:16,320 --> 00:27:20,220
may actually exceed that of my auntie's.

418
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:21,500
What do you mean?

419
00:27:21,500 --> 00:27:24,760
Duke of Hedong's Manor sent you to offer the betrothal gifts, but not only will the marriage be refused,

420
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:26,540
you even go back with a lawsuit.

421
00:27:26,540 --> 00:27:29,620
Ultimately, if Duke of Hedong's Manor is angry,

422
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:32,890
your rice bowl will be smashed!
(T/N: You will lose your job!)

423
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:36,740
My good niece, what do you think should be done then?

424
00:27:37,500 --> 00:27:39,290
About today's incident,

425
00:27:39,290 --> 00:27:41,860
neither Auntie nor Madam Matchmaker should be blamed.

426
00:27:41,860 --> 00:27:43,710
Just blame...

427
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:46,990
Just blame my own bad luck.

428
00:27:46,990 --> 00:27:49,490
Not only that I can't help relieve Father's trouble,

429
00:27:49,490 --> 00:27:53,420
I even entangle the family with such a difficult matter.

430
00:27:53,420 --> 00:27:55,770
If we are embroiled in a lawsuit,

431
00:27:55,770 --> 00:27:59,970
I can't even atone for my guilt even with death.

432
00:27:59,970 --> 00:28:03,100
Therefore...

433
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:10,510
Therefore...

434
00:28:23,470 --> 00:28:27,610
Daughter, just say it then.

435
00:28:30,300 --> 00:28:33,640
Therefore, Shanhu

436
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,950
is a person with poor luck!

437
00:28:35,950 --> 00:28:38,290
I do not deserve to be loved by both manors.

438
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:42,230
Both of your manors are noble families. You meet each other frequently.

439
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:44,690
Because of me, a person of poor luck,

440
00:28:44,690 --> 00:28:46,690
if you end up to be in enmity,

441
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:49,500
wouldn't it be a loss over something trivial?

442
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:55,010
Both of your manors want to elevate my daughter, it's too bad

443
00:28:55,010 --> 00:28:58,560
that my daughter has bad luck and is not fortunate,

444
00:28:58,560 --> 00:29:01,160
and she is abandoned by both of your manors.

445
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:05,340
Both of you, what are we to do?

446
00:29:13,190 --> 00:29:14,730
You...

447
00:29:17,250 --> 00:29:19,900
To avoid gossip in the future

448
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:22,760
leading to damages to the reputation of both manors,

449
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:26,470
I, Shanhu, will pledge an oath right here.

450
00:29:26,470 --> 00:29:29,840
In this whole lifetime,

451
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:33,070
I will never become a concubine at your manors.

452
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:34,560
Forget it, forget it then.

453
00:29:34,560 --> 00:29:39,220
Our Pei Yan will soon go to his new job.

454
00:29:39,220 --> 00:29:41,730
How can he marry someone

455
00:29:41,730 --> 00:29:44,980
who will be so unlucky as to bring a lawsuit?

456
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:48,060
Duke of Hedong's Manor is such a noble household.

457
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:52,440
How can they marry a woman that is even scorned by the Commandant Manor?

458
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:55,140
Let's go back, and  I will report to Heir Apparent.

459
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:58,550
The heir apparent will definitely want to protect the prestige of Duke of Hedong's Manor

460
00:29:58,550 --> 00:30:00,520
and choose another marriage.

461
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:09,040
I... Auntie...

462
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:12,600
Madam Matchmaker!

463
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:14,840
Madam.

464
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:17,430
Take along the betrothal gifts. Go back to the manor.

465
00:30:18,230 --> 00:30:20,840
Bring the betrothal boxes. We're leaving!

466
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,860
- Stop it.
- I'm so angry.

467
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:44,460
This feels good.

468
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:47,040
It is indeed a rare treasure.

469
00:30:52,630 --> 00:30:58,170
[Spring Flower]

470
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:06,590
Master, Ruyi Resist Dye Shop just sent over someone with a message.

471
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:10,030
They said that they'll accept the order of the screen that you want.

472
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:13,930
They also said that you will be satisfied. Otherwise, they won't accept any payment.

473
00:31:15,890 --> 00:31:20,830
It appears that porcupine-like artist won't have to marry.

474
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:24,050
Master, you are pleased, so it's because of that?

475
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:30,540
If she gets married, who will work on the birthday gift for my teacher then?

476
00:31:30,540 --> 00:31:32,370
Will you do it?

477
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:40,090
Anything else?

478
00:31:40,090 --> 00:31:41,620
No, no.

479
00:31:49,370 --> 00:31:51,370
[Hall of Sunset Pool]

480
00:31:51,370 --> 00:31:54,870
I wonder why Your Highness the Crown Prince is here at the Hall of Sunset Pool?

481
00:31:54,870 --> 00:31:56,310
A'Sheng.

482
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:14,200
I passed by the imperial garden just now and saw that it needed to be abandoned by its parents.

483
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:17,380
It fell down the tree and was on the brink of last breaths. Although I saved it,

484
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:19,360
I don't know how to feed it and raise it.

485
00:32:19,360 --> 00:32:21,950
I wonder if I could ask Talented Lady Wu to take care of it.

486
00:32:21,950 --> 00:32:23,790
Since Your Highness is willing to trust me,

487
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:27,090
just leave it at the Hall of Sunset Pool and keep me company then.

488
00:32:27,090 --> 00:32:29,650
You are so lucky to run into the crown prince.

489
00:32:29,650 --> 00:32:32,360
Your Highness, why don't you bestow it a name?

490
00:32:36,530 --> 00:32:38,430
How about calling it Bao'er?

491
00:32:38,430 --> 00:32:40,230
Bao'er.

492
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:44,530
Song Tao, hurry and put Bao'er in a warm place.

493
00:32:44,530 --> 00:32:46,190
Feed it some food and water.

494
00:32:46,190 --> 00:32:50,060
Remember, be gentle; don't hurt it.

495
00:33:10,670 --> 00:33:13,560
I didn't know that Talented Lady Wu was a female Zhuge.
(T/N: Zhuge Liang was a famous strategist and politician during the Three Kingdoms)

496
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:16,080
You can actually predict wisely and foresee the consequences.

497
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:18,900
If I had listened to Talented Lady Wu's advice,

498
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:23,060
I wouldn't have been in such an awkward embarrassment in the Imperial Study.

499
00:33:23,630 --> 00:33:27,920
Everyone thinks that blood relations are the closest to people.

500
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:32,990
It's not necessarily so. Just like the cuckoo birds.

501
00:33:32,990 --> 00:33:35,510
Does Your Highness the Crown Prince know what the first thing

502
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:38,580
- that a cuckoo bird would do once it's hatched?
- What is it?

503
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:42,690
It's to push all the other eggs out of the nest to fall from the tree to their deaths.

504
00:33:42,690 --> 00:33:45,910
It's to ensure that it will have enough food to grow up.

505
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:51,620
How could its parents bear seeing their children kill one another like that?

506
00:33:52,690 --> 00:33:54,940
Why can't these young birds live peacefully together?

507
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:57,440
Isn't it better to help each other and love each other?

508
00:33:57,440 --> 00:34:01,800
Crown Prince, don't forget what Laozi said, "Doing nothing is effective as doing things by following nature's flow."

509
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:06,120
Furthermore, something in this world cannot be shared.

510
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:08,400
Such as the crown prince's seat,

511
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,890
and the emperor's throne.

512
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:19,830
Hearing Talented Lady Wu's remarks I can reap a lot of knowledge.

513
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:23,840
The sky is getting darker. I will take my leave.

514
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:27,600
Crown Prince has high aspirations.

515
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,600
What is the point of gaining a temporary advantage?

516
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:33,100
It is still not as good as keeping a low profile and seizing the opportunity.

517
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:36,940
Thank you for your advice, Talented Lady Wu.

518
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:39,150
Take care, Your Highness.

519
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:47,840
[Hall of Sunset Pool]

520
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:04,400
Your Highness, where are you going?

521
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,400
To clear out everything to His Majesty.

522
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:10,800
Hasn't Talented Lady Wu just said that you should be keeping a low profile and quietly wait for an opportunity?

523
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:13,400
You should reflect upon that!

524
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:17,000
[Hall of Immortal Dew]

525
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:35,600
Shouldn't I give him a little respect at least?

526
00:35:35,600 --> 00:35:38,800
Eunuch Pan, you didn't know about this.

527
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:41,600
Even though Physician Dou is only in charge of epidemic prevention,

528
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:45,400
he has some exquisite embroidery skills.

529
00:35:45,400 --> 00:35:47,200
I finally got ahold of Physician Dou,

530
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:49,800
but the Courtyard of Misfortune deliberately obstructed

531
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:52,000
and hid away that person!

532
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:57,200
Xiao Shunzi must know about what happened.

533
00:35:57,200 --> 00:36:00,600
That's why I want to find out

534
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:03,200
some insider information from Xiao Shunzi.

535
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,800
This is a token of my appreciation.

536
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:16,500
Please accept it, Eunuch Pan.

537
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:21,000
Since it's a token of appreciation from Attire Expert Zhuo,

538
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:23,200
I will accept it then.

539
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:24,600
I have another matter to ask.

540
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:26,200
Speak.

541
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:30,400
You must not allow Sun Decheng to meet Xiao Shunzi.

542
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:33,200
Rest assured.

543
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:36,000
Whatever you lose from Sun Decheng,

544
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:38,500
I will make it up to you.

545
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:40,600
Good, good.

546
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:44,400
Since Xiao Shunzi's case is related to the Bureau of Imperial Attire's official duty,

547
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,600
I will have to handle this affair properly,

548
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:50,100
and give Xiao Shunzi to Attire Expert Zhuo for questioning.

549
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:52,600
Thank you, Eunuch Pan.

550
00:36:55,100 --> 00:36:57,700
Eunuch Pan, Sun Decheng of the Courtyard of Misfortune would like to see you.

551
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,000
Tell him that I'm not here.

552
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,600
But...

553
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:03,800
But he said he has an appointment with you.

554
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,100
There's no such thing.

555
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:08,400
Go tell him that I will take care of Xiao Shunzi's case justly by following the law.

556
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:11,700
I will not play favors. Tell him not to bother me day and night.

557
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:13,000
Yes.

558
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:17,600
Attire Expert Zhuo,

559
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:20,600
I will accompany you to the jail right now.

560
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:23,600
We will question Xiao Shunzi.

561
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:26,200
No hurry.

562
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:29,800
Xiao Shunzi is anxiously waiting for his master to save him now.

563
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:32,400
He probably won't say anything.

564
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,700
Therefore,

565
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:36,920
the best method is to...

566
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,600
don't ask any question,

567
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:42,500
just use the harshest torture.

568
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:44,200
After a day or two,

569
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:47,000
Xiao Shunzi will know his master can't save him.

570
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:51,200
If he wants to live, he'll have to obediently

571
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:53,900
tell me the truth.

572
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:59,000
Attire Export Zhuo, you are truly smart.

573
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:14,100
Eunuch Gao, will His Majesty see me?

574
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:18,790
Crown Prince, it's best that you go back.

575
00:38:18,790 --> 00:38:21,290
Don't make it difficult for this servant.

576
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,700
Why won't His Majesty see me?

577
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:32,200
The matter over Your Highness's proposal to reform the imperial examination system

578
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:34,400
has offended many people.

579
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:38,200
Someone has reported to His Majesty that Your Highness lives an unbridled life

580
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:40,400
and is addicted to imbibing alcoholic drinks.

581
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,900
When did I ever get addicted to drinking alcohol and living an unbridled life?

582
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:45,600
How can His Majesty believe in such rumors?

583
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:49,500
His Majesty has been weak in his health, and he is further obsessed with taking elixir pills.

584
00:38:49,500 --> 00:38:53,800
He is afraid of touching such dirty things as alcohol, that's why he won't see you, Crown Prince.

585
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:56,600
Your Highness the Crown Prince, you should go back for now.

586
00:38:56,600 --> 00:39:00,800
If your cherished body is hurt, this servant will not be able to withstand it.

587
00:39:31,720 --> 00:39:33,360
Talented Lady Wu.

588
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:38,800
Please go inside and tell Eunuch Gao

589
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:41,000
that I will be there just a little late.

590
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,600
Yes.

591
00:39:48,770 --> 00:39:52,460
Your Highness the Crown Prince, since you won't listen to advice, why call me?

592
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:57,500
Talented Lady Wu, you told me to keep a low profile and wait for a good opportunity.

593
00:39:57,500 --> 00:40:00,600
But you didn't tell me, what should I be doing now?

594
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:03,800
Your Highness the Crown Prince, you are young, ambitious, and easily irritated.

595
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:06,000
Why not go back and copy some scriptures?

596
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,600
For one thing, you can cultivate and nurture your temper.

597
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:12,000
Secondly, you can sincerely pray for blessings for His Majesty.

598
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,600
Whatever you want to tell His Majesty,

599
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:17,200
it's better to go back and show him by doing it.

600
00:40:17,200 --> 00:40:21,200
There is the saying that "Sincereity can split open gold and rocks." His Majesty is a wise emperor.

601
00:40:21,200 --> 00:40:25,000
He will sooner or later see how filial Your Highness the Crown Prince is.

602
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:29,000
This is what I meant by keeping a low profile to wait for a good opportunity.

603
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:31,200
Do you understand now, Your Highness?

604
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:04,800
I'm begging you.

605
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:07,600
I haven't shut my eyes for two days and two nights.

606
00:41:13,600 --> 00:41:17,600
As long as you tell us where Physician Dou is,

607
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:21,600
I guarantee that your case will become trivial and you'll be out of trouble.

608
00:41:21,600 --> 00:41:23,800
You won't lose any arms or legs,

609
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:27,600
and go back to work at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

610
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:32,290
This Physician Dou...

611
00:41:32,290 --> 00:41:34,600
He is inside the Courtyard of Misfortune.

612
00:41:35,740 --> 00:41:37,950
The day that I was arrested,

613
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:40,630
I even saw him there.

614
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:45,000
Fine.

615
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:49,370
You can continue to bear this responsibility

616
00:41:49,370 --> 00:41:51,400
for your master and Physician Dou.

617
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:53,800
They are enjoying a good time outside.

618
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:56,300
Who would remember you?

619
00:41:57,600 --> 00:42:01,400
Master, where are you?

620
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:04,240
Why haven't you come to save me?

621
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:06,300
I can't hold on much anymore.

622
00:42:06,300 --> 00:42:08,800
[Directorate of Eunuchs]

623
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:18,000
Eunuch Pan!

624
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:20,400
You scared me.

625
00:42:21,100 --> 00:42:23,200
Isn't this Eunuch Sun?

626
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:26,000
What are you doing in the middle of the night?

627
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:29,800
Eunuch Sun, you are an important person and busy. I have an urgent plea.

628
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:32,200
That's why I couldn't help but wait here.

629
00:42:32,200 --> 00:42:34,200
Is it still for the case of your disciple, Xiao Shunzi?

630
00:42:34,200 --> 00:42:35,600
Yes, yes.

631
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:37,600
Don't worry about that case anymore.

632
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:40,600
Once the case is thoroughly investigated, I will let him go.

633
00:42:40,600 --> 00:42:45,000
You... It's useless to worry.

634
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:50,100
Eunuch Pan, Xiao Shunzi is just a lowly eunuch.

635
00:42:50,100 --> 00:42:52,600
Even if he secretly sold goods from outside the palace, the guilty shouldn't be punishable by death.

636
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:57,000
Sun Decheng, I don't know if you are really muddled or pretending to be muddled.

637
00:42:57,000 --> 00:43:01,200
Originally it wasn't a big crime for Xiao Shunzi to secretly sell private merchandise from outside the palace.

638
00:43:01,200 --> 00:43:03,700
I would have liked to do you a favor and let him go.

639
00:43:03,700 --> 00:43:08,000
But you...

640
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:11,300
You think it over. Who have you offended?

641
00:43:18,380 --> 00:43:20,940
Is it actually Attire Expert Zhuo?

